# Change log

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
This project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).

## [Unreleased][unreleased]

## [0.6.1] - 2015-09-17
### Fixed
- Export Panels.

## [0.6.0] - 2015-09-17
### Added
- Action component.

### Changed
- Compatibility with the new runtime.

## [0.5.1] - 2015-07-25
### Added
- Made `Panels` adapt to orientation changes and browser resizing.
- `width` is a prop of `Panel` now.
- Set a sensible default width (360px) that depends on the viewport.

### Changed
- Extracted the panel's width outside of the its styles.

## [0.5.0] - 2015-07-20
### Added
- Pass default width down to Panel.
- Hide scrollbars altogether.

### Changed
- Removed Radium as we need to use pseudo styles which it doesn't support and our use of it is very
  minimal anyway, so we can do without it.

## [0.4.1] - 2015-07-19
### Changed
- Use Radium from npm as React was removed as a peer dependency.

## [0.4.0] - 2015-07-13
### Changed
- Using Radium for advanced CSS.
- Upgraded to `react@0.14.0-beta1`.

## [0.3.0] - 2015-06-11
### Changed
- Moved blocks into its own package `panels-blocks`.

## [0.2.2] - 2015-06-07
### Added
- `.eslintrc` with rules for babel + React through `babel-eslint`, `eslint-plugin-react`.

### Changed
- `flux` for `panels` props in actions. TODO revisit.

## [0.2.1] - 2015-06-02
### Changed
- Removed ActionWithIcon as we weren't using it.
- Fixed vendor prefixed styles.

## [0.2.0] - 2015-06-02
### Added
- ActionIcon to create an action with an arrow.

## [0.1.6] - 2015-05-30
### Added
- Vendor prefixes for CSS.

## [0.1.5] - 2015-05-30
### Changed
- Allow actions to tell if they are active by comparing themselves to the `nextUri` on a panels
  router keys' structure.

## [0.1.4] - 2015-05-24
### Changed
- Allow actions to hijack `onClick`.

## [0.1.0] - 2015-05-08
### Added

- panels
- panel
- blocks:
  - action
  - action with icon
  - title
  - text
  - subtitle

[unreleased]: https://github.com/UXtemple/panels-router/compare/v0.1.0..HEAD
